t. We also determine several graph\nparameters in these random graphs, such as the chromatic number, small subgraph\ncounts, the diameter, and the independence number. We are also able to\ncharacterise many phase transitions in edge percolation on these random graphs,\nsuch as the threshold for the appearance of a giant component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jun 2019 03:36:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2020 21:22:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 22:37:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 09:40:36 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 14:10:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-23"}
